mg anime course Remastered For CS:S!

A complety rework from my anime course from CS:GO. Enjoy this better version. (maybe in a future in CS:2)

A course and chill mini game to play with friends...or maybe alone.

- Every level has been reworked (of course that room you know is reworked).
- 10 Levels (7 normal and 3 Bonus).

Remember to upload this file in your fast download server not as bz2,Â Just upload it uncompressed, otherwise you won't be able to download it (more than 150mb limit in bz2).
